        Based on the available data, we observed a slight correlation between color and burial depth. As shown in the chart, each color is associated with a specific burial depth. However, the limited number of values in our dataset prevents us from making more conclusive statements about the relationship between color and burial depth.

        Despite these limitations, we believe that our analysis provides some initial insights into the possible relationship between burial practices and the color of wrappings. As we continue to gather more data, we hope to be able to shed more light on this topic.
    </h5>
